    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1267470/extras/0b34af998a9d1297e7cef3e50c580c0e.avif?t=1745569628\" width=600 height=74 /></span><br><br>在《尼罗河勇士》中，玩家将率领被埃及众神祝福的勇士，踏上征途，讨伐贪婪的吞日蛇神阿波菲斯，最终寻回太阳。<br><br>随机变化的关卡及奖励和相比传统更快节奏的战棋相结合，组合出每局都不同的游戏体验。<br>精巧走位，规避伤害；<br>集火输出，减轻压力；<br>选择奖励，强化角色。<br><br>·古埃及风格的游戏背景与人物<br>·快节奏的战棋游戏<br>·三个极具特色的游戏角色<br>·丰富的石板“卡牌”，打造能力各异的人物<br>·随机变化的关卡，体验不一样的单次流程<br>·多种多样的辅助系统<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1267470/extras/e4feab839e04b6b1cab8f4793c7176c5.avif?t=1745569628\" width=600 height=74 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1267470/extras/f1e7e1de0e87652dfce2f604becd9124.poster.avif?t=1745569628\" width=600 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1267470/extras/f1e7e1de0e87652dfce2f604becd9124.webm?t=1745569628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1267470/extras/f1e7e1de0e87652dfce2f604becd9124.mp4?t=1745569628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>◆烈阳勇士◆</strong><br>前排战斗的勇士，既能够抵挡敌人的攻击，也可以成为杀戮的尖刀。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1267470/extras/690809a6b4d310460bd15304c57a4525.poster.avif?t=1745569628\" width=600 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1267470/extras/690809a6b4d310460bd15304c57a4525.webm?t=1745569628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1267470/extras/690809a6b4d310460bd15304c57a4525.mp4?t=1745569628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>◆沙洲猎手◆</strong><br>用弓箭在最安全的地方给予敌人最残酷的一击。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1267470/extras/5650975d9f397011b530ba8bd2b89763.poster.avif?t=1745569628\" width=600 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1267470/extras/5650975d9f397011b530ba8bd2b89763.webm?t=1745569628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1267470/extras/5650975d9f397011b530ba8bd2b89763.mp4?t=1745569628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>◆秘法师◆</strong><br>魔法会撕碎一切。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1267470/extras/c49e1ad1dad7e2b65667107557c53c12.avif?t=1745569628\" width=600 height=74 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1267470/extras/0d9bc1f51b03f63baa81beb3750418dc.poster.avif?t=1745569628\" width=600 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1267470/extras/0d9bc1f51b03f63baa81beb3750418dc.webm?t=1745569628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1267470/extras/0d9bc1f51b03f63baa81beb3750418dc.mp4?t=1745569628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>石板系统</strong> - 每一次胜利后都可以从三个随机石板中选择一个来加强角色，打造属于你的尼罗河勇士小队吧。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1267470/extras/795c6780ee64b1276f293e1cc4f030ca.poster.avif?t=1745569628\" width=600 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1267470/extras/795c6780ee64b1276f293e1cc4f030ca.webm?t=1745569628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1267470/extras/795c6780ee64b1276f293e1cc4f030ca.mp4?t=1745569628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>武器系统</strong> - 通过关卡中获得或者在市场中购入，让角色装备上相对应的武器防具和饰品，根据实际情况切换装备应对不同的战况。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1267470/extras/5ae9a499173b913bc2410ac6b5334908.poster.avif?t=1745569628\" width=600 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1267470/extras/5ae9a499173b913bc2410ac6b5334908.webm?t=1745569628\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1267470/extras/5ae9a499173b913bc2410ac6b5334908.mp4?t=1745569628\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>建造系统</strong> - 扩建你的城市规模，每一个建筑都能带来不一样的永久加成，为你下一次的冒险带来有益的帮助。",
